{
  "video_id": "vB0BiKbHiyA",
  "title": "A Mother’s Promise: You Can Be Yourself | NYT - Conception",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 7300.0,
      "end_time": 10960.0,
      "text": "My husband was an activist from El Salvador."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 10960.0,
      "end_time": 15400.0,
      "text": "One time, he left on a trip in about November"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 15400.0,
      "end_time": 21600.0,
      "text": "and I didn’t hear a word from him until February."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21600.0,
      "end_time": 23640.0,
      "text": "Finally, he called and asked me to meet him"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23640.0,
      "end_time": 26550.0,
      "text": "in Mexico City the next day."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26550.0,
      "end_time": 31440.0,
      "text": "We had about one day and one night together."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31440.0,
      "end_time": 34530.0,
      "text": "I knew that going back to El Salvador"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34530.0,
      "end_time": 36810.0,
      "text": "would be really dangerous."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36810.0,
      "end_time": 41550.0,
      "text": "I also knew that if he couldn’t do the one thing that"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 41550.0,
      "end_time": 45330.0,
      "text": "was the most important to him, that it would be"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 45330.0,
      "end_time": 48570.0,
      "text": "like he wasn’t really living."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 48570.0,
      "end_time": 53310.0,
      "text": "A few weeks after I got home,  I found out that I was pregnant."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 53310.0,
      "end_time": 56650.0,
      "text": "A few weeks after that, I found out"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 56650.0,
      "end_time": 60540.0,
      "text": "that Wilfredo had been killed."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 60540.0,
      "end_time": 65250.0,
      "text": "I was just so glad that he was leaving part of himself"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 65250.0,
      "end_time": 68130.0,
      "text": "with me."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 68130.0,
      "end_time": 73560.0,
      "text": "I named him Daniel, a pseudonym that his father used."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 73560.0,
      "end_time": 77970.0,
      "text": "Having Danny in my life was like having a light."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 77970.0,
      "end_time": 82860.0,
      "text": "I was grieving and then I had this beautiful baby."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 82860.0,
      "end_time": 85870.0,
      "text": "I thought about, even though Wilfredo isn’t here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 85870.0,
      "end_time": 89670.0,
      "text": "how can I raise Danny in a way that would make him proud?"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 89670.0,
      "end_time": 92250.0,
      "text": "But on the other hand,  I didn’t want Danny"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 92250.0,
      "end_time": 98530.0,
      "text": "to feel like he had to replace his father in any way."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 98530.0,
      "end_time": 103730.0,
      "text": "And so I wrote him a letter and I promised him"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 103730.0,
      "end_time": 106700.0,
      "text": "that I was going to let him be who he was"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 106700.0,
      "end_time": 109929.0,
      "text": "and allow him to walk his own path."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 109930.0,
      "end_time": 114600.0,
      "text": "That promise turned out to be really important."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 114600.0,
      "end_time": 118199.0,
      "text": "A few weeks before Danny’s fourth birthday,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 118200.0,
      "end_time": 122520.0,
      "text": "he told me that he wanted to be a princess for Halloween."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 122520.0,
      "end_time": 125640.0,
      "text": "This wasn’t really a big surprise to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 125640.0,
      "end_time": 127860.0,
      "text": "From the time he was 1 and 1/2 years old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 127860.0,
      "end_time": 131760.0,
      "text": "he had this Barbie that he took with him everywhere he went"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 131760.0,
      "end_time": 134910.0,
      "text": "and he loved purple and pink."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 134910.0,
      "end_time": 137430.0,
      "text": "I usually let him do his thing at home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 137430.0,
      "end_time": 143190.0,
      "text": "but in public, I was worried about judgment and teasing."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 143190.0,
      "end_time": 147359.0,
      "text": "I didn’t know if I was doing something wrong as Danny’s mom."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 147360.0,
      "end_time": 149490.0,
      "text": "And I also kind of wondered what Wilfredo"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 149490.0,
      "end_time": 151820.0,
      "text": "would have said or done."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 151820.0,
      "end_time": 155239.0,
      "text": "I say to Danny,  “How about Peter Pan instead?”"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 155240.0,
      "end_time": 159110.0,
      "text": "But Danny was really clear on what he wanted."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 159110.0,
      "end_time": 161560.0,
      "text": "I had to make a choice."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 161560.0,
      "end_time": 165940.0,
      "text": "Would I try to pressure him to be like other boys?"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 165940.0,
      "end_time": 172770.0,
      "text": "We found this big purple lacy dress that had jewels on it"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 172770.0,
      "end_time": 175600.0,
      "text": "and I cut it down to size for Danny"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 175600.0,
      "end_time": 178900.0,
      "text": "and I also found a pink shimmery gown"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 178900.0,
      "end_time": 183480.0,
      "text": "because I decided I could be a princess, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 183480.0,
      "end_time": 187470.0,
      "text": "I had a dream that Wilfredo came back to meet Danny."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 187470.0,
      "end_time": 190650.0,
      "text": "I thought, oh no, what if he sees"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 190650.0,
      "end_time": 193360.0,
      "text": "Danny in his princess dress?"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 193360.0,
      "end_time": 196300.0,
      "text": "And what if he doesn’t accept him for who he is?"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 199210.0,
      "end_time": 204400.0,
      "text": "But I also believe in something pretty fundamental."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 204400.0,
      "end_time": 207850.0,
      "text": "Parents don’t get to decide who their children are."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 207850.0,
      "end_time": 210250.0,
      "text": "What we get to do is to support them."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 213610.0,
      "end_time": 216780.0,
      "text": "I do believe that Wilfredo would have"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 216780.0,
      "end_time": 222900.0,
      "text": "seen that honoring Danny for who he is was important to him."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 225900.0,
      "end_time": 229350.0,
      "text": "Danny is really full of love and heart —"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 229350.0,
      "end_time": 233310.0,
      "text": "something that he got from his dad."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 233320.0,
      "end_time": 239130.0,
      "text": "I would tell him, Danny has not followed exactly"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 239130.0,
      "end_time": 244820.0,
      "text": "in your footsteps, but I can’t imagine that you wouldn’t"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 244820.0,
      "end_time": 249609.0,
      "text": "be incredibly proud of our son."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 249610.0,
      "end_time": 253290.0,
      "text": "He’s one of the bravest people I’ve ever met, just like you."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 263115.0,
      "end_time": 265285.0,
      "text": "My mother Nina —"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 265285.0,
      "end_time": 269235.0,
      "text": "I don't know a lot about her."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 269235.0,
      "end_time": 272115.0,
      "text": "I remember that she was profoundly sad."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 272115.0,
      "end_time": 275435.0,
      "text": "It was sad being around sadness."
    }
  ]
}